summary:
Co-founder of the international marketing agency FABERGE marketing partner.

Economics teacher at Stedelijk College (Eindhoven/Netherlands)

Coach at Vermaat (Utrecht/Netherlands)

Head of the NGO Assembly of cultural exchange of Ukraine /NGO Assembly of cultural exchange of Ukraine/.

Senior lecturer at the departments of the University of Customs and Finance: the Department of International Relations, Regional Studies and Tourism, the Department of Marketing and the Department of Journalism (Dnipro/Ukraine)

Lecturer at the International Marketing Department of the University named after Alfred Nobel.

Organizer of more than 100 festivals and conferences in Ukraine.

Marketing analyst.

Speaker. Media expert.

Marketer. Copywriter.

PR technologist. News editor and community administrator at SMM
 
Ambassador for the city of Dnipro of the project "100 responsible acts of citizens" of the Center for Democracy and the Rule of Law and USAID.

Moderator and official representative of projects of the Higher School of Communications 1+1 media /Dnipro, Zaporizhzhia, Poltava, Cherkasy/.

Author and coordinator of hundreds of advertising campaigns and strategic cases for leading companies of Ukraine.

Dissertation: "Financial Mechanisms of Retail Marketing". Postgraduate student of the Department of Management of Foreign Economic Activities of the University of Customs and Finance.
Co-author and ambassador of the Dnipro ECO AWARENESS educational program.
 
Co-founder, expert and editor of the educational space Media Scientific HUB.
Profile in Google Academy: https://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=uk&user=YHjcBjwAAAAJ

profile_positions.description:
In our unique Exellerator Business HUB project, we have combined the technology and pragmatism of England with the creativity and wisdom of Ukraine.
We have created universal business solutions for those businesses that are ready to move forward and develop.
Everyone dreams of being a Google or Apple company, but not all of them are... We don't guarantee you a tailwind, but we'll set your sails! ...
Finance and marketing are two pillars of business success. Our task is to provide an integrated approach to managing these competencies. We know everything about it, and that is why we guarantee the result. With us, you will get access to a 20-year collection of business cases from international experts.
We work and consult offline in England, the Netherlands, and Poland.
Welcome - we know the answers to all your business questions!
